response.overview: Arriving in the small town of Fallwell, Massachusetts to claim her inheritance, horror hostess Elvira receives a less than enthusiastic reception from the conservative locals -- amongst them, her sinister uncle Vincent, who, unbeknownst to her, is an evil warlock.
response.tagline: Elvira makes her Big Scream Debut in her Hot New Comedy.
response.title: Elvira: Mistress of the Dark
